snippet.title: (A COMPLICATED GAME) BAFF Halloween - Walkthrough FULL GAME (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
BAFF Halloween - Walkthrough FULL GAME (No Commentary)
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Minimalist, hardcore, and challenging game in the avoid-em-up genre with a creepy style that will test your reflexes, timing, and planning! This game is as hard as hell!
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
